{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Zoe Louise</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Zoe Louise articulates the untouchable through painting that leaves the paint 'brush' of bloomed roses on the canvas. Her digital prints on Ordinals lets the light bathe the surface of the artwork. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"600\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/polarity.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/polarity.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/polarity-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/polarity-400x533.jpeg 400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Polarity by Zoe Louise on Ordinals</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"I was wondering if reality could surpass death. Then it occurred to me reality is a process that involves consciousness. Death suffocates consciousness. Yours, not mine. You indeed have surpassed death in my reality.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Zoe Louise</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: A Bouquet of Intimate Passings</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>A Bouquet of Intimate Passings shares a deeply personal collection. \"Death knows no time, no age, or no human. It arrives unsung, often leaving those it spares shaken. In contemplating how to weave this stark reminder into the fabric of life, I embarked on something beautiful.\" There are 28 artworks in the collection, each a singular rose bloom, subsumed with paint. In contrast to the ephemeral nature of life, the collection is minted on Bitcoin in the Ordinals format, so the artists story will always be remembered.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-1024x778.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-1024x778.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-300x228.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-768x583.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-1536x1167.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-2048x1556.png 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-1320x1003.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/zoelouise-intimate-passings-600x456.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>A Bouquet of Intimate Passings by Zoe Louise</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Black Rose</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The artwork 'Black Rose' lives in a five artwork collection by the same name. The charcoaled textures leave only the barest pixels of color to peer through the abyss. IF there was a work that spoke to the depth of loss, then 'Black Rose' is the one. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"736\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-1024x1006.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-1024x1006.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-300x295.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-768x754.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-1536x1509.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-1320x1297.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM-600x589.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-22-at-11.00.07 AM.png 1698w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Black Rose by Zoe Louise</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/melzie-q/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/line398-1-800x600-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/line398-1-800x600-1.png 800w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/line398-1-800x600-1-300x225.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/line398-1-800x600-1-768x576.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/line398-1-800x600-1-400x300.png 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/line398-1-800x600-1-600x450.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Line 398 by Zoe Louise</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/melzie-q/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tZoe Louise | Line 398\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}